b服务器：就是一个容器，里面放着网站文件等 指服务器上运行着的一个软件，可以处理浏览器等Web客户端的请求并返回相应响应，也可以放置网站文件，让全世界浏览；可以放置数据文件，让全世界下载。目前最主流的三个Web服务器是Apache、 Nginx 、IIS。","categories":[{"name":"web安全学习","slug":"web安全学习","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/web%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"}],"tags":[{"name":"web安全","slug":"web安全","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/web%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/"},{"name":"cms","slug":"cms","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/cms/"},{"name":"web服务器","slug":"web服务器","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/web%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/"}]},{"title":"第一篇文章","slug":"第一篇文章","date":"2022-04-02T01:48:06.000Z","updated":"2022-04-02T02:02:31.328Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/04/02/第一篇文章/","link":"","permalink":"http://example.com/2022/04/02/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/","excerpt":"","text":"忙活了一天终于搭建好博客了，我滴个天啊！！！ 冒号后面一定要加个空格！！！","categories":[{"name":"网站建设","slug":"网站建设","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE/"}],"tags":[{"name":"网站","slug":"网站","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"web安全学习","slug":"web安全学习","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/web%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"},{"name":"网站建设","slug":"网站建设","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE/"}],"tags":[{"name":"web安全","slug":"web安全","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/web%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/"},{"name":"cms","slug":"cms","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/cms/"},{"name":"web服务器","slug":"web服务器","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/web%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/"},{"name":"网站","slug":"网站","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/"}]}